name: Simple_Living_7-piece_Burntwood_Dining_Set_
reviews: Love the burnt gray look and fits perfectly in my dinning space; However, table is a little small with all six chairs around it. Would have been great if it had a pull out extension!! Awesome quality..
We love this table perfect fit for tight table are still offering 6 seats. Table was easy to put together, the chairs took about 2 hours for all. The color and finish are great!
Was delivered right on time, easy to assemble, dimensions to size, it's grey color is what I was hoping for and got.
